 to be upset. PSN isn’t available everywhere, and this move could potentially lock players in certain countries out of their game permanently. Players have also expressed concern about the security of their data. Sony recently suffered a data breach, though the information stolen was connected to employees and not customers.\n"}</script><link rel="preload" as="image" imageSrcSet="https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2048x1152/16x11/filters:focal(1024x576:1025x577):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25431967/LaserCannon1_2048x1152.png 16w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2048x1152/32x21/filters:focal(1024x576:1025x577):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25431967/LaserCannon1_2048x1152.png 32w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2048x1152/48x32/filters:focal(1024x576:1025x577):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25431967/LaserCannon1_2048x1152.png 48w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2048x1152/64x43/filters:focal(1024x576:1025x577):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25431967/LaserCannon1_2048x1152.png 64w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2048x1152/96x64/filters:focal(1024x576:1025x577):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25431967/LaserCannon1_2048x1152.png 96w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2048x1152/128x85/filters:focal(1024x576:1025x577):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25431967/LaserCannon1_2048x1152.png 128w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2048x1152/256x171/filters:focal(1024x576:1025x577):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25431967/LaserCannon1_2048x1152.png 256w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2048x1152/376x251/filters:focal(1024x576:1025x577):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25431967/LaserCannon1_2048x1152.png 376w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2048x1152/384x256/filters:focal(1024x576:1025x577):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/